<h2>Thanks for joining Mumsnet</h2>
<p>Please check your email to confirm your account, and you'll be ready to go.</p>
</div>
<div class="form-alert success" data-js="header-blocked-registration-success">
<p>Apologies, but we're not accepting new user registrations at the moment. You're free to browse the site as a guest in the meantime.</p>
</div>
